a2t.text_actual: This camera application will allow you to make excellent pictures very fast and simply, utilizing all advantage of your phone or tablet.  Features: ● Optical/digital zoom ● Screen long press for making photo ● Focus mode(Auto,Infinity,Macro) ● White balance(Auto,Incadecent,Daylight,etc.) ● Exposure ● Disabling shutter sound(may not work on some devices) ● Additional photo effects IF YOU DON'T WANT TO SEE AD BANNERS OR IF YOU WANT TO HELP OUR TEAM IN DEVELOPING OUR EXISTING AND FUTURE APPLICATIONS YOU CAN INSTALL "Donate HD Camera Ultra"(https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.jessdev.donatehdcu)
